  m_text: '<i>Stay on the master path or face ruination! Remember the repeating pattern
    to work out the secret path.</i>


    How to play?


    1. Your goal is to
    walk through all four quadrants of the map.

    2. Move through the first quadrant
    and remember the pattern.

    3. The correct path rotates by 90 degrees in each
    quadrant.

    4. Try to figure out the correct path while it''s invisible.


    Press
    F1 to toggle this popup.

'
